This is a feasibility study testing the use of the Cytosponge cent device in patients with known oesophageal cancer treated with pre-operative or definitive chemoradiation.

 All participants will receive one Cytosponge cent procedure at one time-point within 4-16 weeks after completion of chemoradiotherapy.

